<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Display Solutions</title><link>http://nwazet.com:80/product/display-solutions</link><description>Display Solutions</description><item><title>Four Digit Seven Segment Display</title><link>http://nwazet.com:80/fourdigitsevensegment</link><description>&lt;h2&gt;Product Description&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This nice blue seven segment display provides excellent segment uniformity and is highly visible up to seven meters away. It provides great readability even in bright ambient light. It looks slick with its white segments on a black surface.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Related Components&lt;/h2&gt;

